SSEEEE AALLSSOO
       The full documentation for ffoolldd is maintained
       as a Texinfo manual.   If the  iinnffoo  and
       ffoolldd  programs are properly installed at your
       site, the command

              iinnffoo ffoolldd

       should give you access to the complete manual.



fold 6.7                         December 2006
